    "summary": "在孤岛想象和日常生活中讨论“休闲”的价值。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s1",
      "text": "Imagine staying on an island alone.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p1",
      "tr": "想象一下独自待在一个岛上。",
      "g": "祈使句",
      "d": "Imagine doing sth. 意为想象做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/VQmBc3ouWhc26zdADaJ9Uf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s2",
      "text": "You can only take five things with you.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p1",
      "tr": "你只能随身携带五样东西。",
      "g": "主语 + 情态动词 + 动词原形",
      "d": "can 表示能力；with you 意为随身。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/mfDCnUNxkejuYmeAuTayui.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s3",
      "text": "You might put food, water, tools and clothes on your list.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p1",
      "tr": "你可能会把食物、水、工具和衣服列在清单上。",
      "g": "主语 + 情态动词 + 动词原形 + 宾语",
      "d": "might 表示推测；on your list 在清单上。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/J4hN3RBdg3eArseFLhGcan.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s4",
      "text": "But what about the fifth one?",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p1",
      "tr": "但是第五样呢？",
      "g": "疑问句",
      "d": "What about...? 用于征求意见或询问情况。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/yubRv5XnjVmAyqYy8DUb2i.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s5",
      "text": "Most people would choose something for fun, like a novel, a magazine or a solar media player.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p1",
      "tr": "大多数人会选择一些有趣的东西，比如小说、杂志或太阳能媒体播放器。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 修饰语",
      "d": "would 表示意愿；like 意为比如。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/vFbNXpP9VTpjnNR6JfWMZf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s6",
      "text": "After all, no one wants to get bored!",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p1",
      "tr": "毕竟，没有人想变得无聊！",
      "g": "状语 + 主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "After all 意为毕竟；get bored 变得无聊。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/pBLyLCAZttEpwWrpUeeinf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s7",
      "text": "Fun can do away with bad feelings and lift our spirits.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p2",
      "tr": "乐趣可以消除负面情绪，振奋我们的精神。",
      "g": "主谓宾结构",
      "d": "do away with 消除；lift spirits 振奋精神。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/TKrgn7hFuangRY5Z63WXwG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s8",
      "text": "Just picture yourself watching a funny film on that island.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p2",
      "tr": "试想一下你在那个岛上看一部有趣的电影。",
      "g": "祈使句",
      "d": "picture yourself doing sth. 想象你自己正在做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/hps2qUVVYrjpa4txoXHxaf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s9",
      "text": "Sitting under the trees will not be boring at all.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p2",
      "tr": "坐在树下一点也不会觉得无聊。",
      "g": "动名词作主语",
      "d": "not...at all 一点也不。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/qFPJ59NP7tmhkCwNxFAwdX.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s10",
      "text": "It becomes a moment of joy.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p2",
      "tr": "它变成了一个快乐的时刻。",
      "g": "主系表结构",
      "d": "moment of joy 快乐的时刻。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/496KMVoYJeNpgwApgg38Ue.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s11",
      "text": "Fun also keeps us feeling youthful.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p3",
      "tr": "乐趣也让我们感到年轻。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 宾语补足语",
      "d": "keep sb. doing sth. 使某人保持某种状态。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/bxT588tpHL6PwWTDskN3dV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s12",
      "text": "As George Bernard Shaw once said, \"We don't stop playing because we grow old; we grow old because we stop playing.\"",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p3",
      "tr": "正如萧伯纳曾经说过的：\"我们不是因为变老而停止玩耍；我们是因为停止玩耍而变老。\"",
      "g": "复合句",
      "d": "As 引导定语从句；because 引导原因状语从句。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/rwGeu5Ay8b67GR3RZut6Z5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s13",
      "text": "Research also shows that fun brings people closer.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p4",
      "tr": "研究还表明，乐趣让人们走得更近。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语从句",
      "d": "that 引导宾语从句。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/2WMJWTM6yAGnthvyUPRy3R.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s14",
      "text": "No one is an island.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p4",
      "tr": "没有人是一座孤岛。",
      "g": "主系表结构",
      "d": "经典比喻，强调社交的重要性。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/gQVBBBx366VwNURocFXLR9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s15",
      "text": "Having fun is a good way to connect with others.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p4",
      "tr": "寻找乐趣是与他人建立联系的好方法。",
      "g": "动名词作主语",
      "d": "connect with 与...建立联系。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/Xii7N88fPPhw5M6rZGFS3R.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s16",
      "text": "So, next time, invite your friends to enjoy live music together.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p4",
      "tr": "所以，下次邀请你的朋友一起欣赏现场音乐吧。",
      "g": "祈使句",
      "d": "invite sb. to do sth. 邀请某人做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/u5Bsfb8q7jrkxpQHf4qvxB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s17",
      "text": "It's not just about having fun – you will be closer because of the shared experience!",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p4",
      "tr": "这不仅仅是为了好玩——你们会因为共同的经历而变得更亲近！",
      "g": "并列复合句",
      "d": "because of 因为（后接名词短语）。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/MmnhcpiSpXpGAoZyUx2ziW.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s18",
      "text": "Fun is important in a number of ways.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p5",
      "tr": "乐趣在很多方面都很重要。",
      "g": "主系表结构",
      "d": "in a number of ways 在许多方面。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/noGPxRVmxzeweh5DHZZJYF.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s19",
      "text": "Don't forget to take some time out to have fun and enjoy life!",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p5",
      "tr": "别忘了抽点时间去寻找乐趣，享受生活！",
      "g": "祈使句",
      "d": "forget to do sth. 忘记要做某事。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/FXmy7TzQ2tFp7k7SR8T46j.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-article-s20",
      "text": "We need to work hard. But we should be able to play hard, too.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-article-p5",
      "tr": "我们需要努力工作。但我们也应该能尽情玩耍。",
      "g": "主谓宾结构",
      "d": "need to do sth. 需要做某事；be able to 能够。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/3i542khE7ijCzjDhxiD2Z2.mp3"
    }
  ],
